cards.name: The Fool
cards.upright: Beginnings, openness, trust in the unknown.
cards.flavor_text: The step before the path is known.

cards.name: The High Priestess
cards.flavor_text: What is known without being spoken.

cards.name: The Emperor
cards.flavor_text: The shape that holds the weight.

cards.name: The Hierophant
cards.flavor_text: The path worn smooth by many feet.

cards.name: Strength
cards.flavor_text: Power that does not need to shout.

cards.name: Justice
cards.flavor_text: The scale that remembers all weight.

cards.name: Death
cards.flavor_text: The door that only opens one way.

cards.name: The Devil
cards.flavor_text: Chains that remain because they are held.

cards.name: The Tower
cards.flavor_text: What falls when it can no longer stand.

cards.name: The World
cards.flavor_text: The path that closes the circle.
